From Michael Taffe Subject Re Good Reasons to Wave at each other In article David Gibbs writes But on a similar note for a while I drove a VW Wesfalia this is their camper van I found that other drivers of this same model would wave to me and I waved Maybe its because we were all driving a funny looking vehicle No it is more because van drivers need a little support for driving such underpowered pathetic and truly utilitarian Me and my ' used to wave and be waved at all across the country between NH and Now that we live in though I find you'd have to damn near wave your arm off to keep up with all the van drivers This is truly vee dub peace Taffe Mike Taffe Disclaim This